               </div>
             </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/music" class="group relative col-span-1 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-indigo-900 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
             <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-900"></div>
           </div>
           
           <div class="relative z-10 p-8 min-h-[320px] flex flex-col justify-between">
             <div class="self-end p-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full text-2xl shadow-lg border border-white/10">
               ðŸŽµ
             </div>
             <div>
               <br>
               <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Soundscape</h2>
               <p class="text-indigo-200 text-sm">Heavy Rotation & Favorites</p>
             </div>
           </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/movies" class="group relative col-span-1 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-rose-950 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 bg-rose-800"></div>
           
           <div class="relative z-10 p-8 min-h-[320px] flex flex-col justify-between">
             <div class="self-end p-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full text-2xl shadow-lg border border-white/10">
               ðŸŽ¬
             </div>
             <div>
               <br>
               <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Cinema</h2>
               <p class="text-rose-200 text-sm">Reviews & Watchlist</p>
             </div>
           </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/tech" class="group relative md:col-span-2 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="relative z-10 p-8 md:p-10 min-h-[250px] flex flex-col justify-center items-start">
             <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
               Technical Blog
             </span>
             <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
               Thoughts on Code & Physics
             </h2>
             <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
               Deep dives into Julia, numerical methods, and open source philosophy.
             </p>
